   Yahata, Noriaki and Kawakubo, Yuki and Liu, Xiaoxi and Kawamura, Yoshiya
   and Sasaki, Tsukasa and Kasai, Kiyoto and Yamasue, Hidenori},
Title = {{Neural correlate of autistic-like traits and a common allele in the
   oxytocin receptor gene}},
